# Marziale Design System

When building pages that should look like the marziale.tech homepage, follow this style guide.

## Core Visual Identity

### Colors
- **Primary Background**: `#2563eb` (vibrant blue)
- **Text Color**: `#fff` (white)
- **Window Background**: `#c0c0c0` (Windows 95 gray)
- **Window Header Gradient**: `linear-gradient(90deg, #000080 0%, #1084d0 100%)` (navy to blue)
- **Window Body**: `#fff` (white)
- **3D Border Light**: `#dfdfdf`, `#fff`
- **3D Border Dark**: `#000`, `#404040`
- **Success Text**: `#000080` (navy)
- **Error Text**: `#800000` (dark red)

### Typography
- **Primary Font**: `"W95FA", "MS Sans Serif", "Microsoft Sans Serif", Geneva, sans-serif`
- **Font CDN**: `https://fonts.cdnfonts.com/css/w95fa`
- **Base Size**: 11px for retro windows, responsive elsewhere
- **Desktop Scale**: ~2x for readability (22px)
- **Use `clamp()` for responsive sizing**: e.g., `clamp(0.65rem, 1.5vw, 0.8rem)`

### Aesthetic
- **Theme**: Retro Windows 95/97 meets modern minimalism
- **Pixelated SVG art** for branding and figures
- **Draggable desktop icons** with text captions below
- **Modal windows** with 3D beveled borders and gradient title bars

## CSS Patterns

### Box Model Reset
```css
* { box-sizing: border-box; }
```

### Body Base
```css
body {
    margin: 0;
    height: 100vh;
    overflow: hidden;
    background: #2563eb;
    color: #fff;
    font-family: "W95FA", "MS Sans Serif", "Microsoft Sans Serif", Geneva, sans-serif;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
}
```

### Retro Window (modal/dialog)
```css
.window {
    position: fixed;
    background: #c0c0c0;
    color: #000;
    border: 2px solid;
    border-color: #dfdfdf #000 #000 #dfdfdf;
    box-shadow: 2px 2px 0 #404040;
    font-family: inherit;
    font-size: 11px;
}

.window-header {
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, #000080 0%, #1084d0 100%);
    color: #fff;
    padding: 3px 6px 4px 6px;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #000;
    cursor: grab;
}

.window-close {
    background: #c0c0c0;
    color: #000;
    border: 1px solid;
    border-color: #fff #404040 #404040 #fff;
    cursor: pointer;
    padding: 0 6px;
    font-family: inherit;
}

.window-body {
    padding: 12px;
    background: #fff;
    border: 1px solid #808080;
    margin: 2px;
}
```

### Desktop Icon
```css
.desktop-icon {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.25rem;
    background: transparent;
    border: none;
    padding: 0.5rem;
    cursor: pointer;
    user-select: none;
}

.desktop-icon img {
    width: clamp(2.5rem, 6vw, 3.5rem);
    height: clamp(2.5rem, 6vw, 3.5rem);
    object-fit: contain;
}

.desktop-icon .caption {
    font-size: clamp(0.65rem, 1.5vw, 0.8rem);
    color: #fff;
    text-shadow: 0 1px 2px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
}
```

### Retro Button
```css
.btn {
    background: #c0c0c0;
    color: #000;
    border: 2px solid;
    border-color: #fff #404040 #404040 #fff;
    padding: 4px 16px;
    font-family: inherit;
    cursor: pointer;
}

.btn:hover {
    background: #d4d0c8;
}

.btn:active {
    border-color: #404040 #fff #fff #404040;
}
```

### Retro Input
```css
input, textarea {
    padding: 4px;
    border: 2px solid;
    border-color: #404040 #fff #fff #404040;
    font-family: inherit;
    background: #fff;
}

input:focus, textarea:focus {
    outline: 1px dotted #000;
}
```

## Responsive Breakpoints

- **Mobile**: `max-width: 700px`
- **Desktop**: `min-width: 701px`
- Use `clamp()` for fluid sizing between breakpoints

## File Structure

```
project/
├── index.html
├── style.css (or inline <style>)
├── app.js (if needed)
└── assets/
    └── (icons, images)
```

## Required Resources

1. **Font**: Add to `<head>`:
   ```html
   <link href="https://fonts.cdnfonts.com/css/w95fa" rel="stylesheet">
   ```

2. **Favicon** (optional): 
   ```html
   <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/assets/brand/favicon.svg">
   ```

## Example: Minimal Page Template

```html
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Page Title</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.cdnfonts.com/css/w95fa" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        * { box-sizing: border-box; }
        body {
            margin: 0;
            min-height: 100vh;
            background: #2563eb;
            color: #fff;
            font-family: "W95FA", "MS Sans Serif", "Microsoft Sans Serif", Geneva, sans-serif;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 2rem;
        }
        h1 {
            font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 4vw, 2.5rem);
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }
        .btn {
            background: #c0c0c0;
            color: #000;
            border: 2px solid;
            border-color: #fff #404040 #404040 #fff;
            padding: 8px 24px;
            font-family: inherit;
            font-size: 1rem;
            cursor: pointer;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        .btn:hover { background: #d4d0c8; }
        .btn:active { border-color: #404040 #fff #fff #404040; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <h1>Page Title</h1>
    <a href="/" class="btn">Back to Home</a>
</body>
</html>
```
